Package edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.figure

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Figure
    A general figure window to display a collection of java swing and swing based components in any specified arrangement.
    FigureExporter
    A set of utilities for performing the steps necessary to export a figure in any of the supported formats.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GraphicFormat
    This enumeration defines the graphic formats that are currently supported to export figures.
